Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:12.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Cherry blossom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.68,0:00:16.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We learned it in\NEnglish class, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.58,0:00:18.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's the English\Nwords for "Sakura".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:20.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:23.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's a painting\Ncalled "Cherry Blossom"...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,at the Central Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.44,0:00:27.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know about that painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:31.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that the masterpiece\Nso admired...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,for it's life-like\Nwithering petals?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.06,0:00:38.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to see it once myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.10,0:00:41.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're going to steal the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:43.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Rather, I'd like you to get it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:44.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Get it back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:50.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,An old man came to me\Nfor help yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.54,0:00:58.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He says that the owner\Nof the museum deceived him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:00:59.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.72,0:01:03.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The old man thought\Nhe signed a contract...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.16,0:01:05.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,to loan "Cherry Blossom"\Nto the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:10.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Later he found out they had\Nswitched the contract to one...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.15,0:01:12.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,that transferred ownership\Nof the painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.86,0:01:18.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What is that?! How mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:23.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The modern art exhibition\Nhas just opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.38,0:01:25.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So during the...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:27.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I get the idea, Seira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:30.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just leave the rest to St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.30,0:01:36.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,New Student Rina.\NA Formidable Enemy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:44.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.66,0:01:46.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I still can't beat this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.47,0:01:47.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.30,0:01:50.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And I've used up\Nthis month's allowance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.71,0:01:53.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.59,0:01:56.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,He's been like that the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:04.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:07.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I think you\Nshould retreat a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:08.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.53,0:02:14.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's from you butting in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:16.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No, dodge those!\NAnd those, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.54,0:02:17.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And those, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.51,0:02:18.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.81,0:02:20.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now, punch!\NNo, dodge again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:21.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!\NKick! Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.88,0:02:23.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Jump! Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:24.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Go now! Do it! Do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:25.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.40,0:02:29.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Quit your yakking!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.44,0:02:34.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're so frustrating.\NHere, let me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.23,0:02:42.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.03,0:02:44.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Bad form.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.67,0:02:46.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Whose fault is that, huh?!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just who the heck are you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Butting into other people's business!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:55.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Your interference ruined my game!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.63,0:02:58.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:05.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"I'm going to the Central Museum\Ntomorrow night...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:07.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,to get Cherry Blossom".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:10.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:14.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's a warning from St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:16.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.59,0:03:21.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're living in this town\Nand you don't know St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:23.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:28.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,How rude! I just moved here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.31,0:03:30.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, she's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.62,0:03:33.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,taller than me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.32,0:03:35.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,and I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I have to think up a strategy!\N-Hey, wait...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.30,0:03:40.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:44.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail, I'll get you\Nfor sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:47.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:51.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, I 'm busy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:55.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-I said hold on!\N-You 're annoying me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:01.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:13.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You 're not very fit, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:14.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.92,0:04:18.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me about St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.40,0:04:23.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?!\NCut it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So, you gonna tell me now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.68,0:04:28.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:31.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:33.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll tell you!\NLet go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.80,0:04:37.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, that hurt.\NI thought I was gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:39.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, did that really hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:45.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail is a girl thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:50.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That means she's a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:51.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:55.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Her true identity is unknown. But she's\Nso sly, that the police can't catch her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:57.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The police can't catch her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:03.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I've made up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Where's the Central Museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:10.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,At Third Ave and Bay Street, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:12.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,OK, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if I was\Na bit rough on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:17.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm Rina Takamiya.\NI'm 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.54,0:05:18.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.31,0:05:21.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.15,0:05:25.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Time to eat, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.56,0:05:26.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:29.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it looks delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.37,0:05:30.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now call Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.80,0:05:44.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.31,0:05:47.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.41,0:05:49.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:51.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hmm? This.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:53.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Those are Tarot cards, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.93,0:05:54.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:58.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering if I can use tarot card\Nfortune-telling to do some new magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like fun!\NWill you try it on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:22.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is anything wrong with that card?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Mama, don't scare us like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.92,0:06:33.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Really, Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:35.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You should keep your mind\Non the task at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:38.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's time for dinner, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:39.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.47,0:06:43.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:46.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you and Meimi\Ndo the things the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm a little worried\Nabout Meimi, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.46,0:06:52.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,According to the cards,\Nshe's in for a bit of an ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:58.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.85,0:07:04.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She'll be all right, because like me,\Nher best feature is her cheerfulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:05.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:09.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And besides, my bad fortune-telling\Nis probably wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.84,0:07:12.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, what's\Nfor dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:16.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Today it's your favorite, beef stew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.36,0:07:17.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.76,0:07:20.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Papa, Mama, I'm gonna start eating!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:21.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:26.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm full.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.50,0:07:39.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I can't today, I've got work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:41.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:48.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.10,0:07:52.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I forgot to ask Papa\Nabout the tarot cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:53.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll just give it\Nmy all today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:05.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Forgive me, for I use\Nno gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:11.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,One...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:15.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Two...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:18.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:38.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.56,0:08:42.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's gonna be great today!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:45.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Meimi, be careful tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:46.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I feel strangely uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.31,0:08:53.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You mean Asuka Jr.?\NHe's nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.36,0:08:59.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Not Asuka Jr., something else.\NSomething else is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:06.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So long as the blessings of God\Nare with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,there's nothing\NSt. Tail can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, I better go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.25,0:09:34.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.62,0:09:37.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is in position.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right, good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.17,0:09:43.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you see someone suspicious,\Ndon't let him get away, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:44.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We found this one loitering.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:45.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Whaa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.45,0:09:46.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Come along!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.22,0:09:48.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm coming,\Nyou don't have to pull me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:51.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:53.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.87,0:09:56.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:10:01.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You're in charge of security?\NWow, you're only in grade school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.72,0:10:04.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm in Junior High and\NI'm the same age as you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:05.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:08.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She insists that she's\Nauthorized personnel...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:10.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,and refuses to move\Nfrom the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.47,0:10:12.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr., this one is a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:23.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Take your filthy hands off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:28.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to stand\Nguard over here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.58,0:10:29.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.66,0:10:34.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I was appointed by the Mayor\Nto investigate St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.33,0:10:37.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You can't go around doing whatever\Nyou want without my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:39.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Mayor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:41.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The Mayor happens to be my Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:47.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Which makes you the Mayor's niece?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:52.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Besides, we've got a lot\Nof our paintings here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.47,0:10:54.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,We can't have a thief breaking in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:55.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.82,0:10:58.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Well, you go ahead and\Ndo what you have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.89,0:11:01.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.20,0:11:04.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:25.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Cherry Blossom"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:28.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's splendid, just as they say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:36.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut it out!\NThat's so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.48,0:11:38.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's all because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.89,0:11:41.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.46,0:11:43.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's St. Tail.\NDon't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic! Switch on\Nthe emergency lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.01,0:11:52.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right! Everyone, check\Nup on your assigned posts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:54.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Cherry Blossom is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:58.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:01.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is a cherry blossom petal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.02,0:12:09.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There are more\Ntrailing off that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.60,0:12:15.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If we follow the trail,\Nwe' ll run into the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:18.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!\NDon't go acting on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay here, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:25.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I have confidence in my legs and my\Nstrength, so I'll go nab the thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:27.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:33.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh shoot! That's her way of\Nthrowing us into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.64,0:12:46.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, maybe that girl has\Nalready caught St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.71,0:12:49.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Could be. That would really\Nmake us look like fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:53.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,All right! We'll follow the\Ncherry blossom petals! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:57.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Darn it, I'm the one who's\Ngoing to capture St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:04.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... pretty good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:07.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,but not clever enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.40,0:13:11.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I wonder who that girl is?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.58,0:13:18.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Here I have with me a piece of cloth.\NNothing up my sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,The masterpiece, Cherry Blossom,\Nthat disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.54,0:13:25.51,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Appear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:34.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.43,0:13:39.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact,\NI didn 't steal it, yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you\Nget away, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:45.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,So, that's the room!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:59.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it! Hold it! Hold it! Hold it!\NI'm the one who's capturing St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"Please keep the supply closet clean."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:06.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:09.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,And just why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:13.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help it.\NThe petals led me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.35,0:14:15.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is St. Tail's usual\Nway of confusing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:18.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Which means you fell for\Nthe same trick every time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.11,0:14:23.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There are more petals.\NLet's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.58,0:14:25.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:31.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Isn't this her usual trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.70,0:14:32.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:34.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You are just worried about\Nyour paintings, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,That's all you're worried about!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? You actually\Nbelieved me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.15,0:14:38.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.25,0:14:41.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What I told you were, obviously,\Nall lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,They say that lying makes a thief!\NEven a thief possesses an ounce of logic!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:57.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is absurd!\NDon 't you forget it!\NIn other words, you're pretty bad\Nat avoiding and dodging things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:04.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's this?\NWe're outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:05.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's something strange going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:09.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Although it's not the right season,\Nthe cherry blossom is in full bloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:12.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.77,0:15:15.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Up there, on top of that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.55,0:15:21.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.85,0:15:23.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail? That's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:28.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good work. I'm taking\NCherry Blossom with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.47,0:15:30.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.31,0:15:37.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'll become a police\Nofficer. And I'll arrest St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No way! If anyone arrests St. Tail,\Nit'll be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.40,0:15:43.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It really doesn't matter\Nwho arrests her, does it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:44.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.74,0:15:45.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nyaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:49.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I know it's not the right season,\Nbut I'll give you two a free show...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,of falling cherry blossom petals!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:56.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,It's Show Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.67,0:16:10.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:28.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.18,0:16:31.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What? Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.40,0:16:39.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's outwitted me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:46.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Humph! She may be a thief,\Nbut she's just a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:50.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If only you didn't get in my way,\NI would have captured her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.14,0:16:54.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You really are so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.32,0:17:26.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.71,0:17:40.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Meimi.\NYou're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:43.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Kyoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Seira... nothing happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.90,0:18:00.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Miss Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:03.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.81,0:18:06.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Miss Haneoka.\NI'd like you to do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:10.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is a new student who will be in\Nyour class. Please take her with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.72,0:18:12.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Sure, I'd be glad to.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Miss Takamiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,"ST. TAIL EXPOSES MUSEUM SWINDLE\NOwner Arrested"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.98,0:18:19.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:24.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,This is Rina Takamiya, a new\Nstudent who has just arrived today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.13,0:18:28.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,She's... yesterday's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:30.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:32.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,I'll become a police officer...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.92,0:18:40.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Please take care of her,\NMiss Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.23,0:18:42.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Uh... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:49.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,You keep staring at me.\NIs there something on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:54.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,No. I'm Meimi Haneoka,\Nglad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.60,0:18:56.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,If you ever need anything,\Njust ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:59.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,-Okay. I do have one question.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.04,0:19:02.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,There's this boy I'd like\Nto meet, named Asuka Jr..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:04.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,Is he at this school?
